{"id":"office-move","description":"A fact that is superseded: the office location changes over time.","events":[{"ts":"2026-01-10T09:00:00Z","content":"The team office is located in Building A, floor 3.","tags":["office","location"]},{"ts":"2026-03-15T09:00:00Z","content":"The team office has moved to Building C, floor 7. Building A is no longer used.","tags":["office","location"]}],"queries":[{"ts":"2026-02-01T00:00:00Z","query":"where is the team office located","expectContains":["Building A"],"expectAbsent":["Building C"],"hops":1},{"ts":"2026-04-01T00:00:00Z","query":"where is the team office located","expectContains":["Building C"],"expectAbsent":["Building A, floor 3"],"hops":1}]}
{"id":"db-choice","description":"Non-temporal recall control: a stable decision that should always surface.","events":[{"ts":"2026-02-01T12:00:00Z","content":"We decided to use PostgreSQL as the primary database for the billing service.","tags":["decision","database"]},{"ts":"2026-02-02T12:00:00Z","content":"The billing service also uses Redis for caching session tokens.","tags":["cache"]}],"queries":[{"ts":"2026-06-01T00:00:00Z","query":"what database does billing use","expectContains":["PostgreSQL"],"hops":1},{"ts":"2026-06-01T00:00:00Z","query":"what is used for caching sessions","expectContains":["Redis"],"hops":1}]}
{"id":"role-change","description":"Superseded role assignment plus a two-hop query linking a person to a project.","events":[{"ts":"2026-01-05T08:00:00Z","content":"Dana is the tech lead of the Atlas project.","tags":["people","atlas"]},{"ts":"2026-05-20T08:00:00Z","content":"Dana stepped down; Priya is now the tech lead of the Atlas project.","tags":["people","atlas"]},{"ts":"2026-05-21T08:00:00Z","content":"The Atlas project is targeting a Q4 launch.","tags":["atlas","roadmap"]}],"queries":[{"ts":"2026-02-01T00:00:00Z","query":"who is the tech lead of Atlas","expectContains":["Dana"],"expectAbsent":["Priya"],"hops":1},{"ts":"2026-06-01T00:00:00Z","query":"who leads the project targeting a Q4 launch","expectContains":["Priya"],"expectAbsent":["Dana is the tech lead"],"hops":2}]}
